snippet.title: SkateBIRD Announce (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/GKjrNbR
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/971030/SkateBIRD/

Drop in, and be a skateboarding bird. Grind on bendy straws, kickflip over staplers, and carve killer lines through a cardboard and sticky tape world. More at http://skatebirb.com
